    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome</h1>
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Welcome to Our Platform</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
            Empowering you with the tools to succeed, this is an intuitive and efficient claims management system
