    </div>
</section>

<!-- About Section Container -->
<section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="about-title">About CMCS</h2>
        <p class="about-intro">
            Welcome to CMCS, the intuitive and efficient claims management system designed to streamline your organization's compensation process. Our platform is built to simplify the way you manage claims, from submission to approval, ensuring a seamless experience for both claimants and administrators.
        </p>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-mission">
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>
                    At CMCS, we believe that managing claims should be easy, not overwhelming. That's why we've created a system that's tailored to meet the unique needs of your organization. Our mission is to provide a user-friendly, customizable, and scalable solution that helps you reduce administrative burdens, increase transparency, and improve overall efficiency.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-values">
                <h3>Our Values</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> We believe that complex processes can be simplified, and that's what we've done with CMCS.</li>
                    <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We're committed to providing a clear and transparent claims management process, from start to finish.</li>
                    <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We're dedicated to staying ahead of the curve, incorporating the latest technologies and best practices into our system.</li>
                    <li><strong>Customer-centricity:</strong> Our customers are at the heart of everything we do, and we're committed to delivering exceptional support and service.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


